VI Misc

*  JIRA is used for project management. 
*  STASH and GitHub is used as code repository. 
*  The WorldBank (http://www.worldbank.org/) is used as our
data source. It is possible that some countries may lack data
in certain years, rendering that there may be blank areas or
zero data points in our visualization charts.

